import Body from "./components/Body"
import Header from "./components/Header"
import './App.css'
import {BrowserRouter, Route, Routes} from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {

  return(
    <BrowserRouter className="app">
      <Header />
      <Routes>
        <Route path={'/'} element={<Body />} />
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}
export default App
